snippet.title: Skye: The Misty Isle - Eye of Odin
snippet.description:
A brief OBS test of our Eye of Odin gameplay feature, in our upcoming game SKYE!

All footage was recorded in Unreal Engine 5's editor and is actual gameplay footage!

Heading to Steam Early Access in 2022.

Join our Discord!
https://discord.gg/SkyeGame

Wishlist the game on Steam!
https://bit.ly/SkyeSteam

www.auroragamestudios.co.uk
